OL,6,FA dad has been banned from every JD
OL,7,FSports and Footasylum store in the
OL,8,Fcountry after attacking staff with a
OL,9,Fmetal bar.
OL,11,FJordan Lytollis had been caught
OL,12,Fshoplifting when he threatened members
OL,13,Fof staff in a Liverpool ONE store with
OL,14,Fthe weapon, warning them: "If you come
OL,15,Fanywhere near me, I'll take your head
OL,16,Foff."
OL,18,FIt came amid a spree of thefts worth
OL,19,Fthousands of pounds at stores across
OL,20,FMerseyside and Greater Manchester.
