OL,3,CDad banned from every JD Sports and
OL,4,CFootasylum in the country after attack
OL,6,FA judge on Tuesday labelled him a
OL,7,F"greedy and violent individual" and
OL,8,Ftold him: "Violence and dishonesty
OL,9,Fseems to be second nature to you."
OL,11,FLiverpool Crown Court heard that
OL,12,FLytollis, of St Helens, attended JD
OL,13,FSports at Crownpoint Shopping Park in
OL,14,FDenton, Tameside, on January 10 this
OL,15,Fyear and stole #400 of clothing after
OL,16,Fremoving security tags from the items
OL,17,Fin question and placing them into a
OL,18,Fbag for life.
