OL,6,FWhen challenged by the manager, who
OL,7,Frecognised him from previous
OL,8,Fshoplifting incidents, the 31-year-old
OL,9,Fbecame aggressive and "got into the
OL,10,Fface" of the employee before leaving.
OL,12,FNardeen Nemat, prosecuting, described
OL,13,Fhow he then stole a further #400 of
OL,14,Fgoods from JD Sports at Rock Shopping
OL,15,FCentre in Bury two days later on
OL,16,FJanuary 12.
