OL,6,FA week thereafter, on January 19,
OL,7,FLytollis and an accomplice entered
OL,8,Fanother branch of the sportswear
OL,9,Fchain, this time at Elk Mill Shopping
OL,10,FPark in Oldham, with the defendant
OL,11,Fselecting a number of items before the
OL,12,Fsecond male took them to the changing
OL,13,Frooms and removed the tags.
OL,15,FWhile they ultimately left without
OL,16,Fstealing the clothing, the dad-of-two
OL,17,Fvisited the Trafford Centre later the
OL,18,Fsame day and took two designer coats,
OL,19,Fvalued at #400, from Footasylum
OL,20,Fwithout paying.
