OL,6,FThen, on January 27, he attended the
OL,7,Fretailer's outlet at the Arndale
OL,8,FCentre in Manchester city centre and
OL,9,Fplaced three tracksuits, worth #180,
OL,10,Finto a bag for life.
OL,12,FHowever, having again been challenged
OL,13,Fby staff, Lytollis replied "don't
OL,14,Ff***ing accuse me of stealing" and
OL,15,Fabandoned the items of stock on the
OL,16,Ffloor before leaving. Around an hour
OL,17,Flater, he returned to Crownpoint
OL,18,FShopping Park and attempted to steal
OL,19,Ffurther goods from JD Sports but
OL,20,Fsimilarly left empty handed after
OL,21,Fbeing confronted by staff.
