OL,6,FThree days later, shortly after 4.30pm
OL,7,Fon February 3, Lytollis entered
OL,8,FFootasylum on Paradise Street in
OL,9,FLiverpool city centre and placed
OL,10,Faround #160 of stock into a bag for
OL,11,Flife. However, he was caught in the
OL,12,Fact of shoplifting by employees and
OL,13,Ftold that he would be banned from the
OL,14,Fpremises.
