OL,6,FHaving been taken into a holding room
OL,7,Fwithin the store, Lytollis began
OL,8,Fsearching the staff only area for an
OL,9,Falternative exit. When he was unable
OL,10,Fto find a route out of the shop, he
OL,11,Fthen armed himself with a metal bar
OL,12,Fand began swinging this weapon towards
OL,13,Fmembers of staff while warning "if you
OL,14,Fcome anywhere near me, I'll take your
OL,15,Fhead off", then damaged a locked door
OL,16,Fin order to escape.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/17
