OL,6,FLytollis finally attended JD Sports at
OL,7,FCables Retail Park in Prescot on March
OL,8,F8 and placed #360 of clothing into a
OL,9,Fbag before running from the store
OL,10,Fwithout paying. He has a total of 26
OL,11,Fprevious convictions for 74 offences,
OL,12,Fincluding burglary and assault
OL,13,Foccasioning actual bodily harm.
