OL,6,FCarmel Wilde, defending, told the
OL,7,Fcourt: "His offending was not to fund
OL,8,Fdrugs or alcohol. Many in this court
OL,9,Fsay that. It is an easy excuse to
OL,10,Fmake, but he was very candid and held
OL,11,Fhis hands up to say that it was to
OL,12,Fprovide for his family. He took the
OL,13,Feasy option to clothe himself and says
OL,14,Fthat he got greedy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/17
