OL,3,CDad banned from every JD Sports and
OL,4,CFootasylum in the country after attack
OL,6,F"He has two children. He knows that it
OL,7,Fis wrong. He perhaps lacks a little
OL,8,Finsight. It may seem like a
OL,9,Fmultimillion pound corporation, but
OL,10,Fthese losses have a dreadful impact on
OL,11,Fthe economy and people's jobs. He does
OL,12,Fexpress his regret.
OL,14,F"He knows that it has to stop, and it
OL,15,Fhas stopped. These offences were from
OL,16,FJanuary and February. In that time, he
OL,17,Fhas taken steps to better himself. He
OL,18,Fhas now completed a three-day course
OL,19,Ffor his CSCS card. He can then work on
OL,20,Flabouring sites and building sites.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/17
