OL,3,CDad banned from every JD Sports and
OL,4,CFootasylum in the country after attack
OL,6,F"He is looking forward to having work
OL,7,Fas a focus and providing for his
OL,8,Ffamily legitimately. It was the shock
OL,9,Fof having a new born baby and then
OL,10,Fanother one so quickly afterwards that
OL,11,Fled him to make these foolish choices.
OL,13,F"The defendant has taken steps to
OL,14,Fobtain qualifications and seek work.
OL,15,FHe does not have any drug or alcohol
OL,16,Fproblems. He accepts that, in the
OL,17,Fpast, he may have dabbled. He has a
OL,18,Ffamily to provide for. He is making
OL,19,Fstrides to become a better father."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/17
