OL,6,FLytollis admitted affray, criminal
OL,7,Fdamage and a total of 10 counts of
OL,8,Ftheft. Appearing in the dock wearing a
OL,9,Fgrey Montirex tracksuit, he shook his
OL,10,Fhead as he was jailed for 27 months
OL,11,Fand handed a criminal behaviour order.
OL,13,FThis will ban him from entering every
OL,14,Fbranch of JD Sports, Footasylum and
OL,15,FBlacks in the UK for the next four
OL,16,Fyears. His partner was meanwhile seen
OL,17,Fin tears in the public gallery as he
OL,18,Fwas led to the cells.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/17
