OL,6,FSentencing, Judge Ian Harris said:
OL,7,F"You have received numerous prison
OL,8,Fsentences in the past, together with
OL,9,Fattempts at community disposals, yet
OL,10,Fno sentence or order seems to stop you
OL,11,Ffrom committing offences as and when
OL,12,Fyou please. Violence and dishonesty
OL,13,Fseems to be second nature to you. You
OL,14,Fhave learned very little, and you
OL,15,Fcertainly were not deterred from
OL,16,Ffurther offending.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/17
