OL,4,CFootasylum in the country after attack
OL,6,F"I note that you were willing and able
OL,7,Fto travel from where you lived in St
OL,8,FHelens to Liverpool or Manchester,
OL,9,Ftogether with an individual on
OL,10,Foccasion. You also had the use of a de-
OL,11,Ftagging device which enabled you to
OL,12,Fsteal without alarms being activated.
OL,13,FYour offending was planned and
OL,14,Fdetermined.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/17
