OL,3,CDad banned from every JD Sports and
OL,4,CFootasylum in the country after attack
OL,6,F"You argued with members of staff. You
OL,7,Fbecame argumentative and aggressive
OL,8,Fwhen staff tried to apprehend you. You
OL,9,Fpicked up a metal bar. You swung the
OL,10,Fbar at the employees many times. When
OL,11,Fanother employee tried to assist, you
OL,12,Fthreatened to take his head off.
OL,14,F"These people were doing their level
OL,15,Fbest to work honestly, unlike you, and
OL,16,Fthis is how you behaved when you were
OL,17,Fchallenged. People working in the
OL,18,Fpublic sector are entitled to, and
OL,19,Fwill receive, the protection of the
OL,20,Fcourts from greedy and violent
OL,21,Findividuals like you."
